{"tid":1665663,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［警世］唔好煲加泰","createTime":"2019-10-20T15:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T03:08:02.000Z","uid":22713,"like":12,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c49995fb4c63c8c8f8f25c8fde9aca5c6f4afd6d","tid":1665663,"uid":22713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:55:32.000Z","msg":"之前有post講過<br />\n國際間唔支持加泰獨立<br />\n我地將自己同加泰綑綁會令國際誤以為我地爭取緊獨立<br />\n之前臨時政府宣言 solomon都暗示左宜家講獨立唔係合適時機<br />\n同埋會模糊焦點 偏離左5 大訴求<br />\n到時中共大條道理出解放軍 美國都愛莫能助<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以我地遊行集會唔可以再拎加泰旗</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n同意請幫推"},{"pid":"7dfe55479ed603bbf63493961c715a94f0eba002","tid":1665663,"uid":22713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:55:55.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"326704ca80d456277a84e04d86ebe7e099a80dc2","tid":1665663,"uid":22713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:56:13.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"00275b6e87bb79e6cf0626164052eb42d01d84e8","tid":1665663,"uid":22713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:56:34.000Z","msg":"3/10<br />\n<br />\n721 831 101"},{"pid":"ce4f84c34b8a40372a41b8c8fe9c70ac589a4aa5","tid":1665663,"uid":22713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:56:51.000Z","msg":"4/10<br />\n721 831 101"},{"pid":"53c46e8cf8cbf41493330e458f1d440630abb865","tid":1665663,"uid":22713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:57:08.000Z","msg":"5/10<br />\n721 831 101"},{"pid":"83bc54375d49eb44664cac36bbcb5e6fcb5efaa7","tid":1665663,"uid":22713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:57:20.000Z","msg":"6/10<br />\n7